name: MintSwapToken
description: MintSwap is the first DEX & NFT marketplace natively on the Mint Blockchain, providing token DEX, NFT trading, and NFTFi functions for Web3 users. MintSwap integrates the entire lifespan of a token — from zero to hero — into one protocol. For developers, MintSwap supports exclusive fair launch mechanics and token management tools built by DeFi’s best; and for general users, MintSwap supports advantageous yield and LP opportunities, built-in social and analytic features, and an easy trading experience.
